Woman on tv: At this time,
law enforcement officials

21:27.053 --> 21:28.552
Are unwilling to say
if this attack

21:28.554 --> 21:30.855
Is connected in any way
to joe carroll,

21:30.857 --> 21:32.923
But as this week marks
the first anniversary

21:32.925 --> 21:35.660
