many people are worried

21:35.662 --> 21:37.428
That his vicious cult...

21:37.430 --> 21:38.663
What the hell?

21:38.665 --> 21:40.798
Looks like there's
a new cult.

21:40.800 --> 21:42.366
Who are they?

21:42.368 --> 21:43.968
Who knows?
