that's for sure.

21:43.970 --> 21:45.703
Frank thinks
it's carlos,

21:45.705 --> 21:48.239
But I think he's
too dumb to pull
something like this off.

21:48.241 --> 21:49.473
Who?

21:49.475 --> 21:53.311
You know, carlos
from havenport.

21:53.313 --> 21:54.378
You should talk
to frank.

21:54.380 --> 21:55.413
He saw carlos once.

21:55.415 --> 21:57.048
I think it was
in the village.

22:01.820 --> 22:03.754
Mendez:
The mta only has cameras

22:03.756 --> 22:05.323
In 40% of all city trains.

22:05.325 --> 22:07.358
That video wasn't luck.
They wanted us to see it--

22:07.360 --> 22:08.826
Performance art.

22:08.828 --> 22:10.227
Phillips: Can you
pull up the video

22:10.229 --> 22:11.228
From the adjoining cars?

22:11.230 --> 22:12.596
Mendez: No. The trains
only have cameras

22:12.598 --> 22:14.231
Every other car,
which they knew.

22:14.233 --> 22:15.433
They're slick.

22:15.435 --> 22:17.101
All right, guys.
What do you got?

22:17.103 --> 22:18.903
The hoodies are
newly purchased,
hadn't been washed.

22:18.905 --> 22:20.071
Sold in souvenir shops.

22:20.073 --> 22:21.505
The mask is
molded silicone,

22:21.507 --> 22:24.041
Hand-painted,
very pro.

22:24.043 --> 22:26.210
All right. Mr. Hardy,
don't be shy.

22:26.212 --> 22:29.213
Are these your cult boys
or a new fan club?

22:29.215 --> 22:30.581
Could be both.

22:30.583 --> 22:31.916
Mike: 37 cult members
were identified
in havenport.

22:31.918 --> 22:33.918
17 were killed,
7 in custody,

22:33.920 --> 22:35.419
5 arrested
in the past year.

22:35.421 --> 22:37.388
Well, that makes 8
known acolytes
still out there.

22:37.390 --> 22:40.057
Mike: Unless those 8
found 8 and found 8 more.

22:40.059 --> 22:42.727
Let's just start
with the 3 on the train.

22:42.729 --> 22:43.861
