surveillance footage?

22:43.863 --> 22:44.995
You guys building
a video trail?

22:44.997 --> 22:46.497
It's the works.
Hopkins.

22:46.499 --> 22:49.767
The 3 hooded men
exit at canal.

22:49.769 --> 22:52.503
We pick them up
on west broadway
going uptown.

22:52.505 --> 22:53.637
And then two
turn right,

22:53.639 --> 22:55.706
One goes solo
eastbound.

22:55.708 --> 22:57.308
More to come.
Most businesses are

22:57.310 --> 22:58.743
