their surveillance footage,

22:58.745 --> 23:00.244
And then we have men
going door to door

23:00.246 --> 23:01.946
With court orders
for the rest.

23:01.948 --> 23:04.382
Can you body scan
the 3 suspects?

23:06.885 --> 23:10.488
These are our
known carrollers.

23:14.192 --> 23:16.794
Let's create pre-viz
for males only.

23:25.170 --> 23:27.505
Ok. One match.

23:27.507 --> 23:30.608
Carlos perez.

23:30.610 --> 23:33.010
He's on our list,
one of our
havenport guys.

23:33.012 --> 23:34.745
He's been mia
for a year.

23:34.747 --> 23:35.846
How sure are you?

23:35.848 --> 23:37.248
It's a 75% match.

23:37.250 --> 23:38.682
That's good enough
for me.

23:38.684 --> 23:40.985
Issue a statement.
Get his face out there.

23:40.987 --> 23:42.586
See if the public can
help identify him.

23:42.588 --> 23:44.021
What about
the other two?

23:44.023 --> 23:45.189
They're new
to the party.

23:45.191 --> 23:47.491
Phillips:
Is this new cult, old cult,

23:47.493 --> 23:51.162
Fan club, copycat,
groupies?

23:51.164 --> 23:54.899
What, mr. Hardy?
Anything?

23:54.901 --> 23:56.500
Yeah. I wish I could
be more help,

23:56.502 --> 24:00.237
But, you know,
I really haven't
kept up with the case.

24:00.239 --> 24:02.273
I'm strictly
civilian now,

24:02.275 --> 24:07.044
So, uh, if there's
nothing else,
I'd like to go.

24:10.515 --> 24:11.582
Ok.

24:17.289 --> 24:19.156
Mike: Hey, ryan.
Where you going?

24:19.158 --> 24:20.491
Home.

24:20.493 --> 24:21.892
We didn't find
them all.

24:21.894 --> 24:23.260
Now they're
recruiting more.

24:23.262 --> 24:24.361
Probably.

24:24.363 --> 24:25.729
It's the anniversary
of joe's death.

24:25.731 --> 24:26.764
This is not
an isolated event.

24:26.766 --> 24:28.065
They were wearing
his face.

24:28.067 --> 24:29.433
They're trying to
resurrect his legacy.

24:29.435 --> 24:30.434
Yeah, probably.

24:30.436 --> 24:31.435
You're walking away?

24:31.437 --> 24:32.570
I considered running.

24:32.572 --> 24:33.571
"ryan hardy
can't stop us.

24:33.573 --> 24:34.572
Joe carroll lives."

24:34.574 --> 24:35.606
Yeah. I got it.

24:35.608 --> 24:37.007
Message delivered.

24:37.009 --> 24:38.909
I want no part
of this, mike.

24:38.911 --> 24:41.111
This is over for me,
all right? I'm done.

25:35.634 --> 25:36.634
[doorbell rings]

25:39.304 --> 25:40.671
I came straight
from work,

25:40.673 --> 25:43.040
So you better
have food.

25:43.042 --> 25:45.175
Carlos perez.
You remember him?

25:45.177 --> 25:46.877
Is he the one
with the 4 I.D.S?

25:46.879 --> 25:47.978
Yeah. You had tracked
him to new york

25:47.980 --> 25:50.814
Using rick ruiz
and tony sanchez.

25:50.816 --> 25:53.117
So carlos is one
of the subway killers?

25:53.119 --> 25:54.618
Person of interest.

25:54.620 --> 25:57.021
Let me boot.

25:57.023 --> 25:58.989
The feds brought
intel on, advisory.

25:58.991 --> 26:00.658
I almost signed up for it,
but then I remembered

26:00.660 --> 26:04.862
I'm a part of the ryan hardy
secret task force.

26:04.864 --> 26:06.030
So is it joe's
old cult?

26:06.032 --> 26:08.566
Carlos is.
The other two,
who knows?

26:08.568 --> 26:10.367
And did you share
what you know
with the bureau?

26:10.369 --> 26:12.336
What, this?
This is a hobby.

26:12.338 --> 26:16.473
5 people were killed.
This isn't a hobby.

26:16.475 --> 26:19.009
Ok. Here we go.
Last intel had carlos

26:19.011 --> 26:20.544
Using the moniker
of ruiz.

26:20.546 --> 26:22.846
I have prints
and handwriting analysis

26:22.848 --> 26:24.148
From several
bad credit cards

26:24.150 --> 26:25.482
Obtained
from his girlfriend.

26:25.484 --> 26:28.118
She had told me
he moved back
to california.

26:31.856 --> 26:34.959
Check robert diaz.

26:34.961 --> 26:36.694
It's a name I pulled
from her place.

26:36.696 --> 26:38.896
Are the feds aware
you found this guy's
girlfriend?

26:38.898 --> 26:41.131
I lost her.
What's the point?

26:45.704 --> 26:49.239
His ruiz I.D.
Has a signature match
to a robert diaz,

26:49.241 --> 26:52.309
Short-term rental application
on avenue d.

26:52.311 --> 26:53.677
He's using
a new fake.

26:53.679 --> 26:55.079
Avenue d, huh?

26:55.081 --> 26:57.014
Hey. Um, now would be
the time to tell

26:57.016 --> 26:58.415
The fbi
this information.

26:58.417 --> 27:00.284
Yeah. You're probably
right.

27:00.286 --> 27:02.686
So, max, thanks a lot
for stopping by.

27:02.688 --> 27:04.221
No cab fare?

27:04.223 --> 27:06.357
Hey. Go to the fbi.

27:06.359 --> 27:07.558
They'll figure it out.

27:07.560 --> 27:08.525
Seriously, ryan,

27:08.527 --> 27:10.227
I know I've been
enabling you,

27:10.229 --> 27:12.496
But, uh, maybe it's time
that we stopped this.

27:12.498 --> 27:15.099
Can you lock up
when you leave? Thanks.

28:05.483 --> 28:07.584
[toilet flushes]

28:08.720 --> 28:10.220
Stop!

28:18.396 --> 28:21.965
No, no, no.
I barely touched you.

28:21.967 --> 28:25.369
Hey! Come on!
Hey! Sit up.

28:35.947 --> 28:36.980
Why you running
from me?

28:36.982 --> 28:38.148
