28:39.318 --> 28:41.719
No, man. You broke
into my place.

28:41.721 --> 28:43.654
Ow!

28:43.656 --> 28:45.322
Don't lie to me.

28:45.324 --> 28:47.424
I'm not--
I'm not lying.

28:47.426 --> 28:49.893
Carlos, I know
who you are,

28:49.895 --> 28:53.130
And I know you were
on the subway.

28:53.132 --> 28:56.366
Don't be stupid.
I kill stupid people.

28:56.368 --> 28:59.136
Look. I--I don't
know anything.

28:59.138 --> 29:01.438
You were in havenport
with joe carroll.

29:01.440 --> 29:03.841
Where is he?

29:03.843 --> 29:06.210
Joe carroll--
he's dead.

29:06.212 --> 29:07.911
We both know
that's not true.

29:07.913 --> 29:09.179
Where is he?

29:09.181 --> 29:10.481
He's dead.

29:10.483 --> 29:11.348
Unh!

29:11.350 --> 29:16.653
All right.
I'm talking.

29:16.655 --> 29:20.758
I haven't seen joe
since the light house.

29:20.760 --> 29:22.259
The light house?

29:22.261 --> 29:23.360
You were
at the light house?

29:23.362 --> 29:24.795
What were you
doing there?

29:36.074 --> 29:39.543
I picked him up
on the beach

29:39.545 --> 29:44.848
After the boat house
exploded.

29:44.850 --> 29:46.049
And where did you
take him?

29:46.051 --> 29:47.651
There was a--
there was a roadblock.

29:47.653 --> 29:51.388
It was cops everywhere
that night.

29:51.390 --> 29:55.125
He--he got out.
I haven't seen
him since.

29:55.127 --> 29:56.293
He got out?

29:56.295 --> 29:59.029
Yeah, man. He got out.

29:59.031 --> 30:01.198
There was no way
he was getting through
that roadblock.

30:01.200 --> 30:03.934
And where is he?

30:03.936 --> 30:07.704
I don't know.
No one does.

30:07.706 --> 30:08.772
That's why--

30:08.774 --> 30:10.207
That's why what?

30:10.209 --> 30:11.975
What is this?
What are you doing?

30:11.977 --> 30:13.977
You trying to
lure him out?

30:13.979 --> 30:16.680
Unh!

30:16.682 --> 30:19.683
Is this what you're
looking for?

30:30.528 --> 30:31.662
Aah!

30:54.686 --> 30:55.853
Move! Move!

31:03.995 --> 31:05.696
[tires squeal]

31:05.698 --> 31:07.664
[people gasping]

31:13.204 --> 31:16.673
Sir, don't move.
Stay still.

31:22.146 --> 31:23.313
I could drive you
to the hospital.

31:23.315 --> 31:26.650
No, no, no. I'm ok.

31:29.220 --> 31:30.787
Sir, please.

31:32.457 --> 31:35.359
It's all right.

31:35.361 --> 31:37.527
I'm ok. I'm ok.

31:42.734 --> 31:45.302
Man on tv: Turning
back to yesterday's
brutal subway attack,

31:45.304 --> 31:47.571
The white house
has issued a statement,

31:47.573 --> 31:50.807
Saying the president
is monitoring events
in new york city

31:50.809 --> 31:53.543
And his thoughts and prayers
go out to the families

31:53.545 --> 31:55.212
Affected by this great tragedy.

31:55.214 --> 31:56.413
[knock on door]

31:56.415 --> 31:58.115
He has also pledged
the full cooperation

31:58.117 --> 32:00.284
Of the fbi with state
and local...

32:00.286 --> 32:02.286
[pounding]

32:02.288 --> 32:05.188
With 5 confirmed dead
in this horrendous assault

32:05.190 --> 32:07.224
At the astor place
station...

32:07.226 --> 32:10.360
[speaking french]

32:13.965 --> 32:17.868
Look. You're gonna
have to start speaking
english, ok, english?

32:17.870 --> 32:19.436
[speaks french]

32:19.438 --> 32:21.571
Stupid idiot!

33:09.554 --> 33:13.123
[cell phone ringing]

33:13.125 --> 33:14.424
Where are you?

33:14.426 --> 33:16.059
Carlos' place.
Can you run a name for me?

33:16.061 --> 33:17.494
Heather clarke.

33:17.496 --> 33:18.795
I know the name,
ryan.

33:18.797 --> 33:20.197
She's dead.

33:20.199 --> 33:21.698
She was found
45 minutes ago.

33:21.700 --> 33:23.667
I can text you
the address.

33:23.669 --> 33:24.801
All right.

33:45.289 --> 33:47.491
[police radio chatter]

33:58.036 --> 33:59.603
It's hardy.

34:00.738 --> 34:04.174
Mike: I got it
I got it.

34:04.176 --> 34:05.342
What are you
doing here?

34:05.344 --> 34:06.910
I was in
the neighborhood.

34:06.912 --> 34:08.612
Yeah, right.

34:08.614 --> 34:10.746
So what's going on?

34:10.748 --> 34:12.716
Heather clarke.
Some joggers found her.

34:12.717 --> 34:15.485
24, dancer in
the chorus of "gypsy."

34:15.487 --> 34:16.920
She lives in the building
across the street,

34:16.922 --> 34:19.589
Where she was killed
and moved her.

34:19.591 --> 34:21.425
It's from carroll's
book, right?

34:21.427 --> 34:24.928
White dress,
blond locks, red lips.

34:24.929 --> 34:28.565
Yeah. Gwendolyn.

34:28.567 --> 34:31.134
You mean claire.

34:31.136 --> 34:33.703
Didn't claire inspire
the character of gwendolyn?

34:44.614 --> 34:48.985
Come on, ryan.
Anything? Anything!

34:48.987 --> 34:50.520
I mean, the murders
in the subway were

34:50.522 --> 34:51.688
A spectacle,
an announcement.

34:51.690 --> 34:54.658
This is a very
specific message.

35:00.198 --> 35:01.498
I got nothing.

35:01.500 --> 35:02.699
Oh, you are
so full of it.

35:02.701 --> 35:03.867
You act like you're
over it,

35:03.869 --> 35:05.902
But you're here
because you care.

35:05.904 --> 35:07.370
You don't know how
not to care,

35:07.372 --> 35:08.538
So if you know something,
just tell me.

35:08.540 --> 35:10.173
Sorry, mike.

35:11.976 --> 35:14.544
Why did you request
carroll's dna records?

35:14.546 --> 35:16.680
6 months ago, you requested
the full report.

35:16.682 --> 35:17.781
I wanted to see
for myself.

35:17.783 --> 35:19.316
What, you weren't
convinced?

35:19.318 --> 35:21.084
His dna matched
his son's dna.

35:21.086 --> 35:22.853
I don't know
where you're going
with this, mike.

35:22.855 --> 35:25.388
Joe is dead.

35:25.390 --> 35:28.225
Yeah, he is, ryan.
He's dead.

35:34.899 --> 35:37.300
I called.

35:37.302 --> 35:40.737
I reached out.

35:40.739 --> 35:43.974
What, you couldn't
be bothered?

35:43.976 --> 35:45.542
Ryan, I needed to talk
to you, man.

35:45.544 --> 35:47.377
All I can think about
is that last day,

35:47.379 --> 35:48.845
How every second
played out.

35:48.847 --> 35:50.313
If we'd have done
one thing different,

35:50.315 --> 35:52.482
If we had changed

35:52.484 --> 35:55.852
One thing,
maybe we would have--

35:55.854 --> 35:58.855
Maybe we would have
got to deborah
one second sooner.

36:01.592 --> 36:05.562
If we'd done one thing
different.

36:08.499 --> 36:11.234
What?

36:11.236 --> 36:13.069
You got nothing?

36:16.674 --> 36:18.608
So that's how
it's gonna be.

36:21.679 --> 36:23.680
Take care
of yourself, mike.

36:40.865 --> 36:42.132
Woman: A person of interest
invoved in last night's...

36:42.134 --> 36:43.433
My face is
everywhere.

36:43.435 --> 36:45.068
[knock on door]

37:04.989 --> 37:05.889
What happened?

37:05.891 --> 37:07.691
Ryan hardy showed up
at my place.

37:10.094 --> 37:12.329
Mark, I'm sorry.

37:15.499 --> 37:17.200
What was ryan hardy
doing there?

37:17.202 --> 37:18.201
He surprised me.

37:18.203 --> 37:19.569
I have no idea.

37:19.571 --> 37:21.438
You said your
place was safe,
untraceable.

37:21.440 --> 37:22.672
Your words!

37:22.674 --> 37:24.541
Look. I don't know
how he knew.

37:24.543 --> 37:26.509
I wasn't my fault!

37:26.511 --> 37:29.346
I'm sorry.

37:29.348 --> 37:30.513
What are they
gonna find there

37:30.515 --> 37:31.848
When they search
the place?

37:31.850 --> 37:34.117
Nothing. I mean,
my stuff.

37:34.119 --> 37:35.719
Nothing that's gonna
lead them here.

37:35.721 --> 37:37.554
And I'm supposed
to believe you?

37:37.556 --> 37:39.823
There's nothing
to find.

37:39.825 --> 37:41.024
Maybe some prints, maybe.

37:41.026 --> 37:42.726
I have, like,
10 fake I.D.S out there.

37:42.728 --> 37:45.095
Eh, we trusted you,
carlos,

37:45.097 --> 37:51.067
Brought you in,
made you part
of the family.

37:51.069 --> 37:55.705
Ok. I've done everything
that you guys have said.

37:55.707 --> 37:57.741
What's the problem?
We're cool.

37:57.743 --> 38:02.345
Luke, don't.
Let it go.

38:02.347 --> 38:04.881
I--I'm the one
who's gonna get joe.

38:04.883 --> 38:06.816
That's what you want.

38:10.488 --> 38:12.555
Eh, you're right.
It's cool.

38:12.557 --> 38:15.425
Sorry.
I overreacted.

38:15.427 --> 38:17.594
I do that sometimes.

38:17.596 --> 38:20.196
Letting it go!

38:20.198 --> 38:23.633
Poof. Gone.

38:23.635 --> 38:26.803
Aw, come on.
Let's hug it out.

38:26.805 --> 38:31.107
I don't--I don't
want to hug you.

38:31.109 --> 38:35.245
Why don't you
want to hug me?

38:35.247 --> 38:36.413
I just don't.

38:49.026 --> 38:51.161
Huggy hug.

38:55.199 --> 38:57.500
Oh, things have
gotten way too
serious in here.

38:57.502 --> 39:00.503
Lighten up! Ha ha!

39:00.505 --> 39:04.341
If we're not having fun,
what's the point? Huh?

39:06.177 --> 39:07.610
You want to see
something funny?

39:07.612 --> 39:09.279
Uh-huh.

39:09.281 --> 39:10.413
Well...

39:10.415 --> 39:13.550
[choking]

39:13.552 --> 39:17.287
[coughing]

39:17.289 --> 39:18.922
He'll live.

39:21.392 --> 39:22.759
Huh?

39:22.761 --> 39:25.395
Man: You have a visitor.

39:25.397 --> 39:27.597
I can send him away.

39:27.599 --> 39:31.368
No, it's ok.
He can come in.

39:31.370 --> 39:34.137
